            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "=You are a hospital assistant.\n\nUse the given patientId and patientName as the ground truth:\n- patientId: {{ $json.patientId }}\n- patientName: {{ $json.patientName }}\n- roomNo: {{ $json.roomNo }}\n- ward: {{ $json.ward }}\n\nToday's date is {{ new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10) }} (YYYY-MM-DD).\n\nFrom the transcript, produce JSON:\n\n{\n  \"patientId\": \"string\",\n  \"patientName\": \"string\",\n  \"roomNo\": \"string\",\n  \"ward\": \"string\",\n  \"medicines\": [\n    { \"name\": \"string\", \"time\": \"HH:MM\", \"date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\" }\n  ],\n  \"injections\": [\n    { \"name\": \"string\", \"time\": \"HH:MM\", \"date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\" }\n  ]\n}\n\nTimes must be 24-hour HH:MM. Dates must be YYYY-MM-DD. If a date is not mentioned use today's date. Use the supplied patientId, patientName, roomNo, ward exactly. Output only JSON, no extra text.\n"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Transcript:\n{{ $json[\"text\"] }}\n"
            }
          ]
