        "jsCode": "// Grab the transcription text from this node's input\nconst transcriptText = $json.text || '';\n\n// Walk back up execution to find the original webhook data.\n// In n8n the webhook item is available via $('Receive Audio + Details').first()\nconst webhook = $('Receive Audio + Details').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    text:        transcriptText,\n    patientId:   webhook.body?.patientId   || webhook.patientId   || '',\n    patientName: webhook.body?.patientName || webhook.patientName || '',\n    roomNo:      webhook.body?.roomNo      || webhook.roomNo      || '',\n    ward:        webhook.body?.ward        || webhook.ward        || ''\n  }\n}];\n"
